'''天主教布拉薩維爾總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Brazzapolitana}}；{{lang-fr|Archidiocèse de Brazzaville}}）是[[剛果共和國|剛果共和國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄八個教區。該總教區是該國唯一一個總教區。

'''法屬剛果宗座代牧區'''於1886年6月4日設立，1955年9月14日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXIII |year=1956 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=113-119 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421185405/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-21 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

總教區管轄包括首都[[布拉薩維爾|布拉薩維爾]]和[[普爾省|普爾省]]的[[恩加貝縣|恩加貝縣]]，2006年時有431,225名教友（佔轄區總人口56.9%）、四十個堂區和104名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|亞諾多列·米兰多|Anatole Milandou}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 01.02.2001 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/02/01/0068/00188.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-04-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421184559/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/02/01/0068/00188.html |archivedate=2020-04-21 |language=it |date=2001-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，助理總主教為{{link-fr|比恩維努·馬納米卡·巴福阿庫阿烏|Bienvenu Manamika Bafouakouahou}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 18.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/18/200418a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421175948/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/18/200418a.html |archivedate=2020-04-21 |language=en |date=2020-04-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

